<ofx:section xmlns:ofx="http://www.openfuxml.org" id="how">
	<ofx:title>Maven</ofx:title>
	<ofx:section>
		<ofx:title>Linux (Debian Wheezy)</ofx:title>
		<ofx:paragraph lang="en">
			Get Maven from http://maven.apache.org/download.cgi
		</ofx:paragraph>
		
		<ofx:listing>
			<ofx:raw>
				cd /opt
				tar -xvzf path_to_download/apache-maven-3.1.0-bin.tar.gz
			</ofx:raw>
		</ofx:listing>
		<ofx:paragraph lang="de">
			Danach muss folgender Eintrag in der Datei /etc/profile vor dem Befehk export PATH hinzugef√ºgt werden.
		</ofx:paragraph>
		<ofx:listing>
			<ofx:raw>ATH=$PATH:/opt/apache-maven-3.1.0/bin</ofx:raw>
		</ofx:listing>
	</ofx:section>
	<ofx:section>
		<ofx:title>OSX</ofx:title>
		<ofx:paragraph lang="en">
			Install Homebrew and follow the instructions during the setup script.
		</ofx:paragraph>
		<ofx:listing>
			<ofx:raw>
				ruby -e "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.github.com/Homebrew/homebrew/go/install)"
				brew install maven
			</ofx:raw>
		</ofx:listing>
	</ofx:section>
</ofx:section>